          <text>in<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Food Security Act of 1985/s:1001/ss:h">subsection
			 (h)</cato:entity-ref>, in the second sentence, by striking<quote>or other entity</quote>and
			 inserting<quote>or legal entity</quote>.</text>
        </paragraph>
      </subsection>
